    “answer”: “1) Posture: Sit tall. Unclench jaw. Tongue to roof of mouth.\n2) Rate: 4-second inhale, 6-second exhale through the nose × 10 breaths.\n3) Check-in: Ask: Am I deciding from fear or from clarity?\n4) Frame: Name Self, Vision, Surroundings in one sentence each. Decide.”,
